Paleo Fried Cauliflower Rice

20 min
$8
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Egg

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

AmericanAsian

Course:

Main DishSide Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyVegetarian

Description

A healthy, low-carb alternative to traditional fried rice that’s packed with veggies and flavor!

Ingredients

  • cauliflower: 1 medium head
  • carrot: 1, diced
  • green peas: 1/2 cup
  • green onion: 2, sliced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • egg: 2, beaten
  • coconut aminos: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
